summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from Arthur J. Weaver and Maude H. Weaver, his wife, and Lawrence M. Weaver and Lydia C. Weaver, his wife, to certain lands situated in section 2, township 22 north, range 8 east, W.M., and sections 26, 28 and 30, township 22 north, range 9 east, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating from the Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund, the sum of $2,300.00 in payment for said land.
